c: 2
v: 267
t: "Mwebwe mwemeye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, nimutange muri birya vyiza mwasoromye hamwe nivyo twabakuriye kw’Isi, kandi ntimwipfuze gutanga ibintu bibi mugihe kubwanyu mubihawe mudashobora kuvyakira kiretse nahone mutabiravye uko bimeze, rero nimumenye yuko Imana ifise amatungo kandi ihayagizwa hose"